---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="The Pix's web">
  <section id="Welcome" class="h-screen p-8">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-full p-8 border-8 border-white rounded-lg itmes-center shadow-glow"
    >
      <img
        class="transition-all animate-float w-44 max-md:w-20 max-lg:w-30"
        src="/favicon.svg"
        alt=""
      />
      <h1
        class="mt-8 font-bold text-center text-white text-8xl max-md:text-3xl max-lg:text-6xl"
      >
        I'm <span class="text-glow">Pix</span> a <span class="text-glow"
          >Fullstack</span
        > developer
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    id="AboutMe"
    class="w-screen h-screen p-8 max-md:text-center max-md:p-0 max-md:pt-8"
  >
    <h1 class="my-8 text-6xl font-bold text-white text-glow">About me</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-col w-screen max-md:justify-center">
      <p class="w-1/2 text-white max-md:w-full max-md:mx-4">
        Just a Colombian guy with a dream, the dream to be the best full-stack
        developer, I'm just a kid sitting in his chair, programming, I don't
        know much about this, but I'm willing to learn, I will do everything
        that is necessary to make my dream come true.
      </p>
      <p class="w-1/2 mt-4 text-white max-md:w-full max-md:mx-4">
        I was born with a keyboard in the hand, I'm interested in the technology
        since I was born, always seeing what I will play today?, what I will
        download today? What I will learn today?
      </p>
      <p class="w-1/2 mt-4 text-white max-md:w-full max-md:mx-4">
        And now, <span class="text-glow">you know me?</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
